		<h2><a href='http://itc.conversationsnetwork.org/shows/detail4608.html'>Ted Morgan - Growth of Location</a></h2>
		<div class="summaryImage summaryImageLeft"> 
		  <a class="clickthroughUrl" href="http://itc.conversationsnetwork.org/shows/detail4608.html"> 
		    <img src="http://assets.conversationsnetwork.org/showimages/4608.jpg" width="100" height="125" 
		      title="Image courtesy O'Reilly Media, Inc." 
		      border="0"></a>
		</div>
		<div class="efsSummary">8000 location-based applications around the world and this number will more than double by the end of the year, Ted Morgan claims. The incorporation of location-based features accelerates growth in the mobile space.  Ted Morgan started Skyhook, an innovator in location-based services, which helps app developers expand the mobile experience of their users. Morgan talks about the growing reliance of the public on location-based services and how app developers can leverage this phenomenon.</div>
		<div class="efsMetadataRow">
		  <div class="uglyHackInLieuOfClear" style="height:0.8em"></div>
		  <div id="player-4608" class="centerColPlayer">
