		<h2><a href='http://itc.conversationsnetwork.org/shows/detail4735.html'>Jeff Papows - The Impact of Faulty Software</a></h2>
		<div class="summaryImage summaryImageLeft"> 
		  <a class="clickthroughUrl" href="http://itc.conversationsnetwork.org/shows/detail4735.html"> 
		    <img src="http://assets.conversationsnetwork.org/showimages/4735.jpg" width="100" height="125" 
		      border="0"></a>
		</div>
		<div class="efsSummary">Dr. Moira Gunn talks with author and former Lotus Development President, Jeff Papows, about the three forces which create software glitches, how they are effecting society at large, and how we can fix them.</div>
