		<h2><a href='http://itc.conversationsnetwork.org/shows/detail4638.html'>Kathy Sierra - Creating Passionate Citizens</a></h2>
		<div class="summaryImage summaryImageRight"> 
		  <a class="clickthroughUrl" href="http://itc.conversationsnetwork.org/shows/detail4638.html"> 
		    <img src="http://assets.conversationsnetwork.org/showimages/4638.jpg" width="100" height="125" 
		      border="0"></a>
		</div>
		<div class="efsSummary">Kathy Sierra examines how to create passionate citizens by inviting people to understand the dynamics of passion. Drawing on an interest in the brain and artificial intelligence, developed during her days as a game developer (Virgin, Amblin&#039;, MGM), Sierra explains what is necessary to instill and excite passion.  From the perspective of an engineer she applies the formula and provides a solution to develop not only the product of passion but a passionate end user as well.
